<Defs>
	<ThingDef ParentName="BaseMechanoid">
		<defName>AM_Starfire</defName>
		<label>starfire</label>
		<description>The Starfire mechanoid is a massive tank-like machine, equipped with a powerful cannon that fires very slow-moving unstable singularities. These singularities are generated by a complex fusion reactor at the heart of the machine, which channels and amplifies energy from nearby stars via microscopic skipgates. When fired, the singularities unleash devastating amounts of energy, capable of obliterating entire structures in a single blast, as well as creating secondary energy discharges that arc to nearby targets. The Starfire is heavily armored and equipped with advanced targeting systems, allowing it to rain destruction from afar. However, due to the intense energy requirements of the singularities, the Starfire is only deployed in the most extreme situations, where its destructive power is needed to turn the tide of battle.</description>
